cat << EOF
Net_SMPP_Client is a package for communicating
with SMPP servers, built with
Net_SMPP. It can be used to send SMS messages,
among other things.
Features:
- PDU stack keeps track of which PDUs have
crossed the wire
- Keeps track of the connection state, and
won't let you send PDUs if
the state is incorrect.
- Supports SMPP vendor extensions.
EOF

